product.name: Universal Thread Women's High-Rise 90's Straight Jeans - (US, Numeric, 8, Regular, Regular, Dark Wash)
product.description: Update your denim closet with these High-Rise '90s Straight Jeans from Universal Thread. Made from stretchy denim fabric for flexible comfort, these flattering high-rise jeans feature a straight-leg cut to give you a comfortable retro look. The belt-loop waistband with a fly button offers a secure fit, while multiple front and back pockets let you store your small on-the-go essentials.
product.bullet_points:
• Straight-leg silhouette
• Denim fabric with stretch
• Button and zip fly closure, belt loops
• Classic 5-pocket design
• Item Length Description: Ankle length
